---
title: HelloHero: Rustic Plant-Based Mince & Rosemary Pie with Hidden Veggies & Parmesan Mash Topping
description: Plant-based mince and rosemary have always been the flavour couple to beat and there’s nothing that can surpass them when baked into a golden pie. The homestyle aromas will have your heart and taste buds singing praises all the way through dinner.

